@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
class Account {
  +boolean status
  +boolean id
  #long amount
  -Date email
  +String phone
  +processQuantity()
}
class Teller {
  -Date address
  #int description
  #float code
  -String score
  +calculateType()
  +processQuantity()
  +cancelCreatedat()
}
abstract class Statement {
  #boolean amount
  +double updatedAt
  +savePhone()
  +sendQuantity()
  +findLevel()
  +sendDuration()
}
interface Loan {
  #Date type
  #int address
  +processDescription()
}
class Deposit {
  #int active
  -double type
  #String email
  +Date level
  #Date address
  +sendCreatedat()
  +cancelQuantity()
  +createAmount()
}
class Branch {
  -float total
  +Date note
  #long type
  +long name
  -float active
  +calculateDuration()
  +createCode()
}
Teller --> Statement : "0..1"
Branch --|> Deposit
Statement ..|> Teller
Loan --o Account
note right of Account : Banking domain
@enduml